            <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-snug">Homes renovated and resold</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black leading-none mb-2" style="color:#1e88e5; font-family:'sahar','Open Sans',sans-serif;">20 yrs</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-snug">Of home-flipping experience</div>
